    "body": "I would rather use an overlay solution instead of adding more configuration to the setup.\r\n\r\nSomething like a new yaml file, and include this in the `COMPOSE_FILE` env list.\r\n```\r\n---\r\nversion: \"3.4\"\r\nx-logging: &logging\r\n  logging:\r\n    driver: json-file\r\n    options:\r\n      max-size: 10m\r\n      max-file: \"3\"\r\n\r\nservices:\r\n  data-transport-layer:\r\n    volumes:\r\n      - <PATH ON LOCALHOST>:/db\r\n  l2geth-replica:\r\n    volumes:\r\n      - <PATH ON LOCALHOST>:/geth\r\n```\r\n\r\nUsing host path mapping involves localhost issues I'd rather avoid in an example deployment üòÅ ",
